  <p>For this client, their current online store was not functioning at the payment stage and she needed a redesign of her website. Her website had beenc created over a decade ago and she couldn't edit any products and customers couldn't finish the buying process. I researched the variety of solutions and we decided on the optimal solution technology wise taking into account the budget, timeframe, advantages and disadvantages. </p>
