<section class="problem">
  <h2>design process üë©‚Äçüíª</h2>
  <p>My process for freelance clients begins with a discovery meeting to deeply understand their business needs and current situation. Once we choose a direction, I scope the project and sent for her approval. To start the design I work back and forth with the client to audit their brand and create a moodboard of the feel of the website. Next, we go through websites on the market to understand their design preferences and build a common design language. Next I create a style guide for the website with colors, fonts and snippets of the future UI. Once this is approved, I create three mockup options and let the client choose the direction. From here, I move into final prototypes and ultimately the development phase. In this case, I created a custom Shopify store, but development varies case by case.</p>
</section>

