<section class="problem">
  <h2>what i've <br>learned üìö</h2>
  <p>The biggest lesson I've learned through freelance work is that deeply understanding and listening to business challenges is the priority over the design itself. Often a client needs a business partner in strategy, not just a designer. This client on their previous website couldn't use other payments methods outside of Paypal so understanding this pain and offering solutions to take many payment providers was a huge first win. </p>
</section>

